ganga/python/Ganga
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1) fixed bug #64073: schema evolution problems with lists

2) fixed bug #64080: GangaBox error message

3) changed logic of activating monitoring plugins: use all plugins which match all patterns defined in
the config, rather a first pattern only

For example: the following configuration 

[MonitoringServices]
Executable/LCG = MyMonitoring
*/* = YourMonitoring

will activate both MyMonitoring and YourMonitoring for Executable/LCG jobs and YourMonitoring for
all other jobs. [old logic would not activate YourMonitoring for Executable/LCG jobs]


